com.robindrew.common.io.data

Interface IDataReader

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.io.DataInput
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ByteArrayDataReader, DataReader

    public interface IDataReader
extends java.io.DataInput, java.lang.AutoCloseable
    The Data Set Input interface provides advanced stream reading capabilities.
